com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface LinuxLocalService

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
RedhatLinuxLocalService, SUSELinuxLocalService
All Known Implementing Classes:
LinuxLocalServiceImpl, RedhatLinuxLocalServiceImpl, SUSELinuxLocalServiceImpl
public interface LinuxLocalService
extends com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability

A representation of the model object 'Linux Local Service'.

The following features are supported:

  • Executable Path
  • Service Account
  • Service Description
  • Service Name
  • Service Status
  • Startup Run Level Five
  • Startup Run Level Four
  • Startup Run Level One
  • Startup Run Level Six
  • Startup Run Level Three
  • Startup Run Level Two
  • Startup Run Level Zero
  • Startup Type

See Also:
OsPackage.getLinuxLocalService()
